name: Mars Card 11 - 'Lunch, Ruined (Campbell's Soup'
description: To celebrate the history-making flight on a world other than Earth in April 2021, here is the 11th in a set of tradeable cards to be released by SMART | Pop Artist which features a blend of his painting ‘Lunch, ruined (Campbell’s Soup)’ with NASA’s black and white image from Ingenuity's third Martian flight on April 25th 2021
